{"tid":2125000,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果區一輸左，你八個係千古罪人","createTime":"2020-07-26T00:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T08:29:50.000Z","uid":78184,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b15b275ccfc703a0581e34196587f8e192cfdb5c","tid":2125000,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T00:58:50.000Z","msg":"人地地區直選個個都搞初選協調，但你八個就踴住去爭區一，以為坐定粒六。連民主黨都退出爭區一呀，好心你八個起碼有個協議，以民調做準，到時退選呀<br />\n<br />\n我話係地聽，民建聯就係睇死你地出八個選區一，一陣有區佬唔投票/票數平均分布，咁民建聯就執到死雞。<br />\n<br />\n如果非保皇黨有380席都係區一輸俾民建聯，你八個就係千古罪人，你八個就係同敵人一樣！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">邊個參選區一，好好諗清楚係咪要做千古罪人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"02b27623cdd848307751af22c13fb9f275bacd80","tid":2125000,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c8488c15a4686fb375945303fb867a36acef8ed","tid":2125000,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:04:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"738711f3b48b91fa2e4dddf0e72b72d3c5d99d0c","tid":2125000,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da108dd6eb45444d29436da62f64c5fc4d7f847e","tid":2125000,"uid":65201,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:07:44.000Z","msg":"五毛分化POST，拉"},{"pid":"9bb79d43439e813619b66511ec029957826a8591","tid":2125000,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d8a8e4785dba0260e05d1cea92ef5e2e7acf250","tid":2125000,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95e0807d4acfe519fb8b515dec12542c58b1e0d9","tid":2125000,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"一係就大事幫佢幾個宣傳<br />\n叫大家唔好投佢地任何一個<br />\n日日宣傳<br />\n不過佢地麻Q煩浪費晒大家既時間"},{"pid":"fec6ae105d37628f5c15843edd5a3728663afc47","tid":2125000,"uid":78184,"like